296
00:31:20,400 --> 00:31:22,197
Canne à pêche.

297
00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:26,476
C'est bon.

298
00:31:26,520 --> 00:31:28,988
Tiens. Prends ça.

299
00:31:31,080 --> 00:31:32,957
Ça, je connais !

300
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:50,234
